extends base.pug 
block metaElements
    meta(name="robots" content="INDEX, FOLLOW")
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
block style 
    include ../static/css/privacy.css 
block title 
    title AJWS | Privacy Policy 
block content 
    .privacy-container
        .privacy-header
            h1 Privacy Policy
            p.effective-date Effective Date: 08-06-2026
        .privacy-content
            p At <strong>AJ Water Solutions</strong>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect information when you use our website, book services, purchase products, or communicate with us through our website, WhatsApp, email, or other channels.
            
            h2 1. Information We Collect
            p We may collect the following information from customers:
            ul
                li Full name
                li Phone number
                li Email address
                li Delivery and service address
                li Order and service details
                li Communication history related to orders, inquiries, and support requests
            p We only collect information that is necessary to provide our products and services.

            h2 2. How We Use Your Information
            p We use the information we collect for the following purposes:
            ul
                li Processing product orders and service bookings
                li Scheduling installation, maintenance, and repair services
                li Delivering products and services
                li Sending order confirmations and updates
                li Providing customer support
                li Contacting customers regarding appointments, deliveries, warranty services, and service reminders
                li Sending important notifications related to purchased products or booked services
                li Improving our services and customer experience
                li Complying with legal obligations
            p We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties.

            h2 3. WhatsApp Communications
            p We may use WhatsApp Business and related services to communicate with customers regarding:
            ul
                li Service bookings
                li Appointment confirmations
                li Order status updates
                li Delivery notifications
                li Installation schedules
                li Maintenance reminders
                li Customer support
            p By providing your phone number, you consent to receiving communications related to your orders, services, and support requests through WhatsApp.

            h2 4. Cookies and Authentication
            p Our website uses essential cookies solely for authentication and security purposes.
            p These cookies help:
            ul
                li Maintain secure user sessions
                li Verify user identity
                li Protect accounts from unauthorized access
            p We do not use cookies for advertising or behavioral tracking.

            h2 5. Third-Party Services
            p We use trusted third-party service providers to operate our business, including:
            
            h3 Vercel
            p Our website is hosted and deployed using Vercel. Vercel may process technical information such as IP addresses, browser information, and request logs for hosting, security, and performance purposes.
            
            h3 Nodemailer and Email Providers
            p We use email delivery services through Nodemailer to send order confirmations, service notifications, and customer communications.
            p These service providers process information only as necessary to provide their services.

            h2 6. Data Security
            p We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
            p While we strive to protect your information, no method of internet transmission or electronic storage can be guaranteed to be completely secure.

            h2 7. Data Retention
            p We retain customer information only for as long as necessary to:
            ul
                li Provide products and services
                li Maintain service history and warranty records
                li Fulfill legal, accounting, and business requirements
                li Resolve disputes and provide customer support

            h2 8. Your Rights
            p You have the right to:
            ul
                li Request access to your personal information
                li Request correction of inaccurate information
                li Request deletion of your personal information, subject to legal or business obligations
                li Request information about how your data is being used
            p To exercise any of these rights, please contact us using the details provided below.

            h2 9. Children's Privacy
            p Our services are not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

            h2 10. Changes to This Privacy Policy
            p We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our business practices, legal requirements, or services.
            p Any updates will be posted on this page along with the updated effective date.

            h2 11. Contact Us
            p If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or wish to request access, correction, or deletion of your information, please contact us:
            .contact-info
                p <strong>AJ Water Solutions</strong>
                p Email: <a href="mailto:omkaraj420@gmail.com">omkaraj420@gmail.com</a>
                p Phone: 7276241430
                p Website: <a href="https://ajwatersolutions.in">https://ajwatersolutions.in</a>
            
            p.ack By using our website, booking services, purchasing products, or communicating with us, you acknowledge and agree to this Privacy Policy.
